\[[CEP] = \frac{1}{2} CE \cdot CP = \frac{1}{2} r^2 \sin x \cos x.\]Let $s$ be the length of $\overline{BC}.$  Then $s = 2r,$ so the area of the semicircle with diameter $\overline{BC}$ is
